abstract: Yani Tseng takes one-stroke lead in Yokohama Tire LPGA Classic.
lead_paragraph: Tseng closed with an eagle and a birdie for an eight-under-par 64 and a one-stroke lead in the Yokohama Tire L.P.G.A. Classic in Prattville.

headline.main: Yani Tseng Leads by One in Alabama
